    "snippet": "Was informed today, from our co-located Supervisory LMR Technician, that one of our repeaters (Stony Point - SW portion of forest) was in need of having it's batteries replaced...",
    "narrative": "Was informed today, from our co-located Supervisory LMR Technician, that one of our repeaters (Stony Point - SW portion of forest) was in need of having it's batteries replaced and if the fire module could assist with this. We assisted a few years back and upon further conversation I learned from our Superviosry LMR Technician that the batteries at the repeater have been in need of replacing since last year. Was also informed that the repeater may work, if there was enough power availbele from the batteries, however, if used repeatly, then there may be complete failure of the communication link. I reached out to our forest's FLT and Safety Manager to inquire if any prior communication had occurred between they and our Supervisor LMR Technician. Both the forest's Safety Manager and District Ranger of this areas had not been notified and had no knowledge that this issues was transpiring.",
