    "snippet": "We have a fire on the Chattooga Ranger district on the Chattahoochee-Oconee National Forest. We use Long Creek repeater and Glassy Mountain repeater as our main communication...",
    "narrative": "We have a fire on the Chattooga Ranger district on the Chattahoochee-Oconee National Forest. We use Long Creek repeater and Glassy Mountain repeater as our main communication sources to dispatch. Both of these repeaters have been not working for months now. Radio issue tickets have been submitted on this issue previous to this incident, about one month ago. Today we had a fire where we needed to use these repeaters. We were unable to make contact both ways with dispatch and dispatch with field resources. This is a safety issue.",
    "immediateAction": "Cellphone was used to try and contact dispatch. But cellphone service is limited.",
