    "snippet": "Florida Interagency Dispatchers missed an urgent call from an NPS dispatcher, who requested immediate clearance of the airstrip at Oasis HB for an incoming Medflight. The initial...",
    "narrative": "Florida Interagency Dispatchers missed an urgent call from an NPS dispatcher, who requested immediate clearance of the airstrip at Oasis HB for an incoming Medflight. The initial call was missed due to an ongoing phone outage.On 10/28, the FICC dispatch main phone lines stopped working. Multiple tickets were submitted, and dispatch was informed that the issue stemmed from voicemail licensing. A temporary solution was implemented to forward the main line to a backup cell phone, which dispatch has been using for over 30 days.On Saturday, increased fire activity resulted in multiple calls coming through the contingency cell phone as dispatchers communicated with cooperators and ground resources. During one of these calls, the call from the NPS dispatcher came in but was missed because the dispatcher was already on another call. Consequently, dispatch had to call the NPS dispatcher back, delaying the response to their urgent request.",
    "immediateAction": "We contacted the aviation officer, who confirmed that there was no activity at Oasis HB today. I then called XXX at NPS to update her, and she informed me that the patient was transported by ambulance instead. While the situation was resolved, the ongoing phone outage continues to pose a potential safety risk.",
