    "snippet": "Alabama dispatch has been experiencing spotty communication with field resources on the Tuskegee Ranger District since the mass Lumen switch over on Nov 1st, 2025. Radio...",
    "narrative": "Alabama dispatch has been experiencing spotty communication with field resources on the Tuskegee Ranger District since the mass Lumen switch over on Nov 1st, 2025. Radio communication have been completely down or intermittent between dispatch and the field since the switch over. Being that the Tuskgeee Ranger District has the highest KBDI's throughout the NF in Alabama and also an active wildfire, not having reliable communications with them is a huge hazard. There is also no time frame for when radio communications will be re established since the district doesn't have any Lumen equipment in place or  on order.",
