    "snippet": "AN UNTIMELY NETWORK/SERVER MAINTENANCE DURING WORK HOURS DURING FIRE SEASON CAUSING A PREDICTED 4 HOUR OUTAGE. THE DAY OF THE OUTAGE WAS AFTER A LIGHTNING EVENT AND WHILE...",
    "narrative": "AN UNTIMELY NETWORK/SERVER MAINTENANCE DURING WORK HOURS DURING FIRE SEASON CAUSING A PREDICTED 4 HOUR OUTAGE. THE DAY OF THE OUTAGE WAS AFTER A LIGHTNING EVENT AND WHILE RESOURCES ARE MOVING ABOUT IN THE FIELD. THE OUTAGE AFFECTED FAMAUTH WHICH HOSTS THE ACCESS TO MOST OF THE ESSENTIAL APPLICATIONS AND PROGRAMS NEEDED TO SAFELY DISPATCH, TRACK, MOBILIZE, AND DOCUMENT ACTIVITY AFFECTING LOCAL, STATE, AND NATIONAL EMERGENCY WILDFIRE RESPONSE AND SUPPORT.",
