    "snippet": "Me and my crew have been working the Monroe Canyon Fire and had previously heard about the catering on the fire being bad, and then few days ago, one of my crew members became...",
    "narrative": "Me and my crew have been working the Monroe Canyon Fire and had previously heard about the catering on the fire being bad, and then few days ago, one of my crew members became ill with symptoms consistent with food poisoning shortly after consuming a meal and then myself and another 2 crew members have symptoms consistent with food poisoning. This situation has raised serious concerns about the safety, handling, and preparation of the food provided. Not only has this impacted the health and wellbeing of my crew, but it has also disrupted our work schedule and caused considerable distress.",
