    "snippet": "Firefighter was driving a chase pickup truck on the dirt road in support of an engine. The chase truck is equipped with an after market On-Track GPS tracking device, installed...",
    "narrative": "Firefighter was driving a chase pickup truck on the dirt road in support of an engine. The chase truck is equipped with an after market On-Track GPS tracking device, installed under the driver side dash. While driving on the dirt road, the On-Track device came loose and fell to the floor, behind the the brake pedal, causing bake pedal to stick and brakes not to work. Driver had to manually dislodge the On-Track device from behind the brake pedal in order to stop the chase truck.The On-Track device was secured with Zip Ties. The concern is that other Fed vehicles with On-Track devices, installed in such manner could experience such unsafe incidents.",
