    "snippet": "Our building and dispatch center switched providers to Lumen. After the switch all outgoing calls from the office had their caller ID show up as the front desk and neighboring...",
    "narrative": "Our building and dispatch center switched providers to Lumen. After the switch all outgoing calls from the office had their caller ID show up as the front desk and neighboring dispatch centers, county dispatches, and the GACC were not able to call the dispatch center, they were getting a busy tone as soon as they dialed in. We had active fires and were ordering aircraft for the fires and our GACC was unable to talk to us.",
    "immediateAction": "I initially created tickets through the computer help desk portal, and was able to get the caller ID issue fixed, but there was nothing they could do about the incoming calls. It was recommended I have another dispatch center put in a ticket themselves to see why they could not call us. Over a week later it seems the tickets from other centers achieved some results as we have not had any issues receiving calls so far.",
