    "narrative": "During IA on 5/14,5/15 and 5/18, the AFMO staffed as Engine Boss/IC on Engine XXX and Engine XX-XX.  The individual's pack test expired around 9 months before staffing the engine for IA.  This is a big liability issue for the area and the State of Alaska.  If he were to go down with any medical issue on the fire, it would become a safety issue for everyone on his engine and the rest of the fire.  It has been an ongoing thing for multiple seasons of him not doing his pack test.",
