    "snippet": "Continuing phone issues for the Virginia Interagency Coordination Center. The 5th Helpdesk ticket for the year was submitted on 4/8/2025 (Ticket # 5224594) for the Center's phone...",
    "narrative": "Continuing phone issues for the Virginia Interagency Coordination Center. The 5th Helpdesk ticket for the year was submitted on 4/8/2025 (Ticket # 5224594) for the Center's phone lines dropping calls and not being able to consistently place calls out. Center staff have been working with CIO who opened a ticket with Mettel. As of 4/10 we still cannot place outgoing calls without them being dropped. We are currently supporting 20 suppression modules, multiple misc. overhead, 2 aircraft as well as forest personnel and prescribed fire operations. The current work around is to have the main dispatch line forwarded to the dispatch duty cell phone and radio communications. These ongoing phone problems have and continue to create inconsistent communication with anyone trying to contact the dispatch center via phone.All tickets associated with this issue: 8669677  3/3/2025 5166157  3/9/2025 2392416  3/16/2025 5208839  3/31/2025 5224594  4/8/2025",
