    "snippet": "On 10/19 at 1630 hours, I was dispatched to a new start on private land in which we have an agreement with and is in our coverage.  While arriving on scene I was unable to reach...",
    "narrative": "On 10/19 at 1630 hours, I was dispatched to a new start on private land in which we have an agreement with and is in our coverage.  While arriving on scene I was unable to reach dispatch on both the Clam Lake and West Fork repeaters well enough to make out what each of us were saying.  I had to rely on cell phone coverage and 1 bar of service to get out.  The cell coverage was spotty and dropped the call numerous times that initial night and the next days to follow.  On 10/21 I attempted another repeater 'Elk Creek' that wasn't on the Great divide district but thought I should at least give it a try.  Elk Creek repeater did not work either. Lat/Long of Bear Lake fire is 46°0.052'N, 90°49.237'W.",
