    "snippet": "It was briefed that there would be an IA zone available even though that zone did not exist. When resources came to get the clone we had to turn them away due to no such clone...",
    "narrative": "It was briefed that there would be an IA zone available even though that zone did not exist. When resources came to get the clone we had to turn them away due to no such clone existing. The safety officer came into the comms unit with a very hostile and unprofessional attitude, demanding that we clone a random set of frequencies into the fires radios. None of these frequencies were approved on the 205 or deconflicted with the numerous fires in the area. This is a significant safety risk and also illegal to do. I believe the safety officer is not taking safety seriously especially considering she is a safety officer.",
