    "snippet": "ODF Team 2 managed this fire without an FBAN without fire behavior forecasts and what to expect. Also did not have a fire weather forecaster either. Was told this team had come...",
    "narrative": "ODF Team 2 managed this fire without an FBAN without fire behavior forecasts and what to expect. Also did not have a fire weather forecaster either. Was told this team had come off a previous fire just before and handled that fire the same without an FBAN. One of our other crews told me that they were out and that this ODF team operates without an FBAN to provide us with expected fire behavior and watch our backs.How can ODF claim these are type 1 teams without FBAN and providing us on the line forecasts on what to expect and when to be concerned about fore growth and weather?Take a look at the ODF IAP's and you will see no forecasts.",
