    "snippet": "DISPATCH CENTERS USE FIRENET AS THEIR MAIN EMAIL AND INTERAGENCY SHAREPOINT SPACE. WE HAVE BEEN ASKING FOR ACCESS FOR NEW USERS AND ADDING ACCESS TO OUR DISPATCH CENTER GROUP...",
    "narrative": "DISPATCH CENTERS USE FIRENET AS THEIR MAIN EMAIL AND INTERAGENCY SHAREPOINT SPACE. WE HAVE BEEN ASKING FOR ACCESS FOR NEW USERS AND ADDING ACCESS TO OUR DISPATCH CENTER GROUP EMAIL SINCE 7/1 AND HAVE BEEN REPEATEDLY BEEN GETTING DENIED, IGNORED OR EXTREMELEY DELAYED RESPONSE BACK. THIS SYSTEM IS IMPERATIVE TO THE DISPATCH CENTER FUNCTIONING PROPERLY AND EFFICIENTLY.",
    "immediateAction": "HAVE PUT IN SEVERAL REQUESTS TO ADD USERS AND UPDATE ACCESS TO THE SHARED EMAIL INBOXES. EMAIL FROM THE FIRENET SUPPORT IS SEVERAL DAYS DELAYED OR NEVER REPLIED BACK TO. HAVE REQUESTED SEVERAL NEW ACCOUNTS AND HAVE BEEN DENIED AND THEN WHEN WE ASK FOR FOLLOW UP, THERE IS NOTNING. WE HAVE TRIED TO RE-ACTIVATE, UPDATE AND CREATE SEVERAL ACCOUNTS AND SEVERAL PEOPLE HAVE GONE ALMOST 2+ WKS WITHOUT GETTING INTO THE GROUP EMAILS OR AN ACCOUNT. WE ARE SUPPORT A TYPE 1 INCIDENT - HORSE GULCH , TYPE 3 INCIDENT - DALTON AND SEVERAL IA FIRES",
